page.title: 02Saturday Homelife. Rotherham
page.content: 08:00 I sit in bed and watch the Wide Awake Club. 10:00 I get up and get dressed and have my breakfast. 10:15 I get washed, brush my hair and clean my teeth. 11:00 I go to town with my mum. 13:30 I come back from the town and have my dinner. 14:00 I go out to play. 15:00 I go and watch the television. 15:15 I go out to play again. 16:15 I have my tea. 16:30 I go out on my bike with my friend. 17:10 I come in and read a book. 17:30 I go and watch television again. 19:30 I go to the pub with my mum and dad 21:00 I go to bed.
